```sql
SELECT 
    COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized') AS category_name,
    SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_items_sold
FROM order_items oi
JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
GROUP BY COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized');
```

-- 02_total_items_returned.sql
```sql
SELECT 
    COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized') AS category_name,
    SUM(DISTINCT r.item_id) AS total_items_returned
FROM returns r
JOIN order_items oi ON r.item_id = oi.item_id
JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
WHERE r.status = 'approved'
GROUP BY COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized');
```

-- 03_return_rates_by_category.sql
```sql
WITH sold_items AS (
    SELECT 
        COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized') AS category_name,
        SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_items_sold
    FROM order_items oi
    JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
    LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
    GROUP BY COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized')
),
returned_items AS (
    SELECT 
        COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized') AS category_name,
        SUM(DISTINCT r.item_id) AS total_items_returned
    FROM returns r
    JOIN order_items oi ON r.item_id = oi.item_id
    JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
    LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
    WHERE r.status = 'approved'
    GROUP BY COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized')
)
SELECT 
    s.category_name,
    s.total_items_sold,
    COALESCE(r.total_items_returned, 0) AS total_items_returned,
    COALESCE(r.total_items_returned, 0) * 1.0 / s.total_items_sold AS return_rate
FROM sold_items s
LEFT JOIN returned_items r ON s.category_name = r.category_name
ORDER BY s.category_name;
